WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:43.759
Subtitles and audio translation will begin later. Please wait for the official start of the video.

00:00:43.760 --> 00:00:49.499
Well, welcome family. Thank you for joining us again tonight. We're going to just get right to praying.

00:00:49.500 --> 00:00:56.959
I've been really busy lately, and I'm so thankful for every single one of you. We're fine. I had to take some days.

00:00:56.960 --> 00:01:13.074
The Lord said, 'You need more time focusing just with me.'And I've poured out and poured out, and I've got to the point where I feel dry and I said, 'I've got to get back underneath that waterfall.'It's personal.

00:01:13.075 --> 00:01:21.679
Just because I dump out with you all doesn't mean I don't keep vertical with him, and I want to make sure I'm hearing him in top shape.

00:01:21.680 --> 00:01:31.328
Keeping my relationship with him above all this other stuff; it doesn't matter to me if it all goes away tomorrow, I still have him.

00:01:31.329 --> 00:01:38.239
And that's what I want to make sure: that we're always good and that in my heart I'm seeking his face.

00:01:38.240 --> 00:01:42.941
There's so much ministry that pulls you every single day, and you can get distracted with it.

00:01:42.942 --> 00:01:48.843
Then you've got family, you've got kids you're raising, you've got a job you're working; there's things that are always pulling on you.

00:01:48.844 --> 00:01:57.079
But I have to make sure that I'm always staying sharp, especially when you're talking to as many people as we do.

00:01:57.080 --> 00:02:03.009
And so I take the time. After the tornado, I was frustrated with that.

00:02:03.010 --> 00:02:12.159
We have power and authority over storms, you know, and God has given us that. As he is, so are we in this world.

00:02:12.160 --> 00:02:24.034
And as we see tornadoes come and they're wreaking havoc and doing all that they're doing and everybody's afraid, I warned you all.

00:02:24.035 --> 00:02:30.349
I said there are storms coming. It's not just in the natural storms, but spiritual storms.

00:02:30.350 --> 00:02:36.479
And there's a lot of you that are still asleep and you say, 'Well, Brandon, you know what?

00:02:36.480 --> 00:02:50.135
Whenever I see a storm and it's a tornado right in front of me, well, I'm just going to be bold and just go out there like David and say, "Who is this uncircumcised Philistine that defies the armies of God?"'No, this tornado or whatever.

00:02:50.136 --> 00:03:04.238
Or, you know, when the plague comes again that I've told you countless times the Lord has warned me about, we must take authority and start to activate that inside of you.

00:03:04.239 --> 00:03:13.776
Psalm 91, Psalm 23, getting it down inside of your heart because of the storm that I've seen over and over.

00:03:13.778 --> 00:03:19.439
Financial storms, financial crisis, major shakings to awaken.

00:03:19.440 --> 00:03:30.878
And the only way you're going to weather the storm is by knowing who you are in Christ, by having a foundation of the word of God down inside of yourself, staying vertical.

00:03:30.879 --> 00:03:45.265
If I'm not here and YouTube was to go away, where will you be? If these other people—there's a lot of you that are baby Christians—but you must learn and have the meat of the word down inside of you.

00:03:45.266 --> 00:03:49.729
You've got to get that backbone like a crowbar. Who are you listening to?

00:03:49.730 --> 00:03:56.375
Who's pouring into your life? I like to listen to Reinhard Bonnke a lot. Reinhard Bonnke is one of my favorites.

00:03:56.376 --> 00:04:08.158
After he prayed for me and laid hands on me that day I told you all, when I was a young man and I got an impartation that day, it changed my life forever.

00:04:08.159 --> 00:04:19.272
And when Reinhard Bonnke prayed for me, he said, 'I put a double portion of the anointing that's on my life on you.'And he laid hands on me and the fire of God—I'm talking a lightning bolt—came out of heaven.

00:04:19.273 --> 00:04:25.917
It felt this way. It shook me. I was like a sack of potatoes on the ground when that happened.

00:04:25.918 --> 00:04:32.679
It changed me when I got up off the floor. And I'm not giving any glory to Reinhard Bonnke.

00:04:32.680 --> 00:04:42.874
Reinhard Bonnke was just a man that was yielded to Jesus. But I always respect my elders and I respect the anointing.

00:04:42.875 --> 00:04:48.919
And there was impartation that day; there was something that happened, there was an exchange.

00:04:48.920 --> 00:04:59.932
And ever since then, between him and Ralph Wilkerson, there has been a stirring on the inside of me, a fire shut up in my bones that you just can't control.

00:04:59.933 --> 00:05:04.336
And do you have that? Do you have to have an impartation from somebody to get that? No.

00:05:04.337 --> 00:05:07.860
You can have it right in the middle of your house right now where you're watching.

00:05:07.861 --> 00:05:15.046
But you've got to get yourself in the river in prayer and worship and seeking him daily.

00:05:15.047 --> 00:05:18.145
Not just on Sundays and whenever they have something at the church.

00:05:18.146 --> 00:05:21.688
You've got to have a personal relationship with Jesus where you're going vertical.

00:05:21.689 --> 00:05:31.591
I told you there's a storm coming. I told you there's a shaking to awaken coming to our nation. We must pray for President Trump.

00:05:31.592 --> 00:05:47.677
As you can see, I told you this is not just the one opportunity that I've seen; there's much more that we have to pray for our president to make it across the finish line of what God has called him to do.

00:05:47.678 --> 00:06:00.075
The enemy would try to kill, steal, and destroy. Right? We know what the devil's mode of operation, his whole plan is.

00:06:00.076 --> 00:06:04.770
So we've got to come against it by the blood of the Lamb. We've got to plead the blood.

00:06:04.771 --> 00:06:15.839
You've got to take communion daily. You've got to seek his face daily. We must work while it is still light, for night is coming.

00:06:15.840 --> 00:06:28.719
It's time for us to get an enthusiasm inside of us, a stirring on the inside of us knowing that the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ is at hand.

00:06:28.720 --> 00:06:37.239
The church must wake up. It's not just about filling pews or chairs at the church, having full auditoriums.

00:06:37.240 --> 00:06:49.839
It's about telling people that it's time to repent and it's time to fall down on our knees before a holy God and get right with him because there's many of you that are about to be left.

00:06:49.840 --> 00:06:56.575
It's time to come to church with a heart of worship and thanksgiving for what he's already done in your life.

00:06:56.576 --> 00:07:08.159
But get ready, for he is about to do something even greater. The greatest outpouring of the Spirit of God is about to hit this earth like we've never seen before.

00:07:08.160 --> 00:07:13.350
What we have seen in the past is nothing compared to what we're about to see.

00:07:13.351 --> 00:07:30.719
And there's many of you that are so lackadaisical in your relationship with the Lord and you're so lukewarm and you don't even realize that the water is getting hot all around you and the pot is beginning to boil and you're in it.

00:07:30.720 --> 00:07:43.540
We see it. And I have such an urgency inside of me every single time I do these broadcasts to warn you that the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ is at hand.

00:07:43.541 --> 00:07:53.918
I shout it from the mountaintops and I shout it in the valleys: Jesus Christ is coming.

00:07:53.919 --> 00:08:02.239
But what are we waiting for? He has long patience for the harvest, his fruit.

00:08:02.240 --> 00:08:07.439
And right now, he said, 'Brandon, I'm not out of patience. I'm out of time.

00:08:07.440 --> 00:08:17.448
This dispensation of grace is coming to an end.'He's had long patience for thousands of years now. But this dispensation of grace is coming to an end.

00:08:17.449 --> 00:08:29.439
The Lord Jesus Christ is coming for his church, but he's coming back for a bride that's without spot or wrinkle, that is sold out to him and not sold out to the world.

00:08:29.440 --> 00:08:35.409
So I want to tell you again and again, you must get your heart right before him.

00:08:35.410 --> 00:08:42.238
It's time to repent. Now I know there's a lot of you that want to know what's going on in the news.

00:08:42.239 --> 00:08:50.615
But the biggest headline I can tell you that's going on in the news is the signs of the times of the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ are all around you.

00:08:50.616 --> 00:09:00.377
Are you looking? Are you watching the alarm bells? The sun is setting on this dispensation.

00:09:00.378 --> 00:09:06.337
I'm telling you, I know beyond a shadow of a doubt. I had a Holy Ghost dream last night again.

00:09:06.338 --> 00:09:10.991
The Lord visited me again last night in my dreams, and he visits me. Those are for me.

00:09:10.992 --> 00:09:15.365
The visions are what I tell you, but I don't tell you about my dreams.

00:09:15.366 --> 00:09:25.365
The Lord visits me and talks to me about my own personal life a lot and talks to me and my wife, and there's an urgency.

00:09:25.366 --> 00:09:32.995
He says there are some things that are about to happen. I've warned you about the economy.

00:09:32.996 --> 00:09:41.959
When was the last time we were together? What did the Lord tell us? We saw so much, all to his glory.

00:09:41.960 --> 00:09:52.633
I want to say everything we see or what we do on this channel is just all for his glory. This isn't about Brandon. This isn't a Brandon show.

00:09:52.634 --> 00:09:59.936
This I believe with all my heart God's put it on us for this generation to be watchmen and watchwomen?

00:09:59.937 --> 00:10:07.999
To tell you what the Lord gives us in prayer so that we can pray and change things. Some of it we can't.

00:10:08.000 --> 00:10:13.305
But my main job is always to come on here and always give God glory in everything I say in word and in deed.

00:10:13.306 --> 00:10:21.470
We give all to the glory of God. Can I miss it? Yeah, we can miss it. We're human.

00:10:21.471 --> 00:10:30.305
We're all saved by grace and we're all trying our best to get out to the other side and hear him say, "Well done, thy good and faithful servant.

00:10:30.306 --> 00:10:38.398
Enter into my rest."And that's what I'm after. But can Brandon Biggs miss it? Yes, I can miss it.

00:10:38.399 --> 00:10:46.319
And anybody that tells you they've never missed it is usually either a liar or something else.

00:10:46.320 --> 00:10:54.436
I'm just telling you, everybody has a chance that we all are working out our salvation with fear and trembling and we're going from glory to glory.

00:10:54.437 --> 00:11:05.518
Every one of us. But I want to tell you my main mission every single time I come on here is to throw out the net and see how many fish I can bring in.

00:11:05.519 --> 00:11:09.309
I told you what was coming by the spirit and the leading of the Holy Spirit.

00:11:09.310 --> 00:11:16.872
I believe with what he showed us last time when we were here. I saw President Trump at the desk.

00:11:16.873 --> 00:11:28.475
I saw a dove with an olive branch in its beak and he was flapping his wings over him and I saw church bells ringing around his desk and the Lord said, "Pray for him."Then we prayed for John Kilpatrick.

00:11:28.476 --> 00:11:44.195
We prayed for Perry Stone. The Lord showed me praying over their health, praying over them—these two men—and then Jentezen Franklin and my friend Billy Burke and these others. The Lord said, "I have much more for them to do.

00:11:44.196 --> 00:11:59.910
Pray for their health that they would be restored with the glory to be restored like Moses, that his eyes did not grow dim."And I saw a renewing like the eagles, that their flesh would not fade with the glory.

00:11:59.911 --> 00:12:04.991
The glory kept them. The glory kept Moses. The glory will keep these men.

00:12:04.992 --> 00:12:09.770
And I saw to pray for them more. So we prayed for them last broadcast.

00:12:09.771 --> 00:12:24.869
Then we prayed for President Trump and the Lord said, "Pray for a protection around him."And I saw that in the days ahead we saw by the spirit of the Lord that the Lord warned us that there would be three Senate seats and it would flip blue.

00:12:24.870 --> 00:12:33.206
The Lord said, "You see this? It's increasing."And I saw it went from one—they would have it by one—to having it by three.

00:12:33.207 --> 00:12:43.159
And he said, "If you don't start praying now, they will win the House and the Senate and your president is in jeopardy even by impeachment."25th Amendment.

00:12:43.160 --> 00:13:01.359
The 25th Amendment. There's so many things that the Lord has brought to us to pray over concerning President Trump and we will continue to do so.

00:13:01.360 --> 00:13:07.251
But the main things I have on my heart right now is your life and your heart.

00:13:07.252 --> 00:13:16.159
Where are you with Jesus? Do you know him? And more importantly, does he know you?

00:13:16.160 --> 00:13:21.331
I'm not talking about your grandma's religion that she used to talk to you about as a little boy.

00:13:21.332 --> 00:13:28.082
You say, "Well, yeah, you know, grandma used to talk about Jesus all the time."I'm talking about a personal relationship with the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:13:28.083 --> 00:13:37.512
Do you know him? If you were to die tonight, where would you spend eternity? There is a heaven to gain and a hell to shun.

00:13:37.513 --> 00:13:49.119
We've heard it all the time, especially if you've been in the church a long time. But this is a true statement.

00:13:49.120 --> 00:13:54.317
The Lord said to go over some of the things I saw when I went to tribulation tonight.

00:13:54.318 --> 00:14:03.198
So, I am being obedient to what he told me to do real quick. So, bear with me. It's 15 minutes, but I'm going to go over this really quick.

00:14:03.199 --> 00:14:16.159
I saw the day that I was on July 6th, 2014, I was taken out of my body and the Lord Jesus Christ came in my room and he took me to tribulation.

00:14:16.160 --> 00:14:27.119
It was one of the most life-changing experiences I've ever had. It shook me like I can't even tell you.

00:14:27.120 --> 00:14:33.434
I went from year to year with him as we would travel into the years of tribulation.

00:14:33.435 --> 00:14:39.999
I saw the day it happens. I saw what happens when the rapture takes place.

00:14:40.000 --> 00:14:46.319
And the Lord allowed me to see it happened at night in America.

00:14:46.320 --> 00:14:57.082
It was not night in other parts of the world, of course, but it was night in America.

00:14:57.083 --> 00:15:01.809
I saw lightning shooting all over the sky. Everything was alive.

00:15:01.810 --> 00:15:09.278
The lightning was just bolting and there was no thunder. It was just a light show.

00:15:09.279 --> 00:15:15.098
And I remember the lady screaming, "The aliens came and got them!

00:15:15.099 --> 00:15:22.239
The aliens!"That's what they... they were deceived. They didn't know where everybody disappeared.

00:15:22.240 --> 00:15:28.862
Everybody from the children that were age 15 and younger were all gone.

00:15:28.863 --> 00:15:33.117
So their mothers were all frantically looking for their children.

00:15:33.118 --> 00:15:42.750
They were screaming through the streets and they were looking and calling out their names and they were in panic looking for the kids that were gone.

00:15:42.751 --> 00:15:50.719
All the mothers were running up and down the street screaming for their children and they were all raptured.

00:15:50.720 --> 00:15:55.485
Now, there's some of you that don't believe in the rapture. That's fine. If you don't want to hear this, click out and go away.

00:15:55.486 --> 00:16:02.387
But I'm telling you, for those that are here and you want to know what's coming, I'm going to tell you. I believe in the rapture of the church.

00:16:02.388 --> 00:16:08.659
I believe in what I experienced and when I went to tribulation, I believe that God is not a wife beater.

00:16:08.660 --> 00:16:13.891
We're not appointed unto wrath. And we are not going to go through the tribulation.

00:16:13.892 --> 00:16:28.879
If you're a believing believer and you have your lamp full of oil—there were ten virgins: five had their lamps full and five didn't—which one are you?

00:16:28.880 --> 00:16:41.274
And I saw believers that didn't have their lamps full of oil and they were not expecting the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ. And they were running frantically yelling.

00:16:41.275 --> 00:16:54.892
And I saw one lady that I knew and she was flipping off the Lord, giving the finger to the Lord, yelling at him because she didn't go. She knew. They knew what happened.

00:16:54.893 --> 00:17:14.498
And I saw pastors that were preaching a compromising word that didn't have a backbone like a crowbar telling the people that they needed to repent and turn from their wicked ways, that they believed and they preached a solid lukewarm grace gospel that everything's about grace, brother.

00:17:14.499 --> 00:17:21.619
And I believe we're all saved by grace. But there is a place where we don't act like we used to.

00:17:21.620 --> 00:17:27.505
The very sins we repented of, we went back to, and you live in there.

00:17:27.506 --> 00:17:41.038
The things that you say, "I was once lost and now I'm found."You say, "I'm back living in it."And you say, "Well, I'm still saved,"but I'm going to tell you, you're mistaken.

00:17:41.039 --> 00:17:48.263
When I saw the people and they were running all over the place screaming and they were so upset because there was no peace.

00:17:48.264 --> 00:17:54.375
The peace that passes all understanding abides in every believer.

00:17:54.376 --> 00:18:03.639
You don't even realize that you wake up every single day and the Holy Spirit's leading you for the first time...

00:18:03.640 --> 00:18:07.562
that prayer covering that was there—and people take it for granted.

00:18:07.563 --> 00:18:17.279
Even the world wakes up every single day and there's a prayer covering that the church brings that is no longer here.

00:18:17.280 --> 00:18:22.719
And they all act crazy. They're burning buildings. They're burning cars.

00:18:22.720 --> 00:18:27.999
They're murdering. They're raping. They're pillaging. It was awful.

00:18:28.000 --> 00:18:40.683
It looked like Sodom and Gomorrah, what I would picture it to be. All nuts. They had no balance at all.

00:18:40.684 --> 00:18:49.219
I saw fires and smoke, burning cars all across the city as the Lord said, "Look."And he never spoke anything.

00:18:49.220 --> 00:18:56.479
He just touched my hand and I perceived everything he was saying. He never had to speak anything. I just could hear him.

00:18:56.480 --> 00:19:01.311
And I went through and I could see the lady screaming because I walked up to her because she could see me.

00:19:01.312 --> 00:19:05.475
That was the only time that somebody could see me in tribulation.

00:19:05.476 --> 00:19:13.038
I walked up to her and I said, "What happened?"And she goes, "Don't you know the Christians are all gone?

00:19:13.039 --> 00:19:19.759
Don't you know they're all gone? The Christians are all gone."She was screaming.

00:19:19.760 --> 00:19:32.558
I saw the Antichrist come on the scene. He came out of it. He came on pretty quickly, and they all had a meeting in Berlin.

00:19:32.559 --> 00:19:37.071
I watched them. They were all in Germany. They went to Berlin—every person.

00:19:37.072 --> 00:19:44.719
There was a table full of leaders, and they were all listening to a man that got out of a Rolls-Royce.

00:19:44.720 --> 00:19:52.798
I saw him. He was dressed to the hilt. He had a suit on that was black and white; it was a beautiful suit.

00:19:52.799 --> 00:20:01.678
It looked like cashmere, I don't know. It was beautiful, with a white shirt and a very nice tailored beard.

00:20:01.679 --> 00:20:10.719
His hair was black. He was a very tailored man with olive skin.

00:20:10.720 --> 00:20:19.038
He sat down at this table and as he spoke, peace flowed out of him.

00:20:19.039 --> 00:20:25.519
It was the most hypnotic feeling I've ever felt as I watched this man.

00:20:25.520 --> 00:20:31.199
Everybody surrendered their nations to him within that one hour.

00:20:31.200 --> 00:20:36.959
Everybody had peace. For the first time in a couple of days, it was anarchy.

00:20:36.960 --> 00:20:42.479
Everybody was acting crazy, but when he spoke, everything was okay.

00:20:42.480 --> 00:20:53.439
It was smooth like butter. I'll never forget the way he pulled.

00:20:53.440 --> 00:21:12.158
But that peace that the church brought—all the years of a prayer covering over the world that you don't even realize because you wake up and you take it for granted, every one of us—when that peace was gone, he brought that peace, a sense of peace that was dingy.

00:21:12.159 --> 00:21:24.558
It didn't feel the same. It had a dinginess to it, but it was something that was similar. It's the way it felt.

00:21:24.559 --> 00:21:37.742
So, I tell you all this because I really truly believe that we're so close to this major event taking place soon. As I saw, this is what the Holy Spirit wanted me to tell you.

00:21:37.743 --> 00:21:47.515
As I looked across, I saw so many Christians that were all gathering—the ones that were left, so-called Christians, that were lukewarm.

00:21:47.516 --> 00:21:54.136
They didn't have their lamps full of oil. They weren't expecting; they didn't have an anticipation.

00:21:54.137 --> 00:21:59.051
Remember the virgins? There were five of them that were anticipating.

00:21:59.052 --> 00:22:04.046
They had their lamps full. They knew the bridegroom was coming. The others didn't.

00:22:04.047 --> 00:22:19.918
They said, "Oh, let's have some of yours."And then they said, "No, okay, we better go buy."And as they were going out and getting theirs, the bridegroom came like a thief in the night, right?

00:22:19.919 --> 00:22:28.220
Those Christians that I saw here were so upset. The pastors that were still here—too much is given, much is required.

00:22:28.221 --> 00:22:37.008
I saw pastors that were once on TBN and Daystar, and I will not use their names ever, that were left here.

00:22:37.009 --> 00:22:51.697
They blamed them for not being taught the gospel. I saw these people who were there, and they started going to the mountains.

00:22:51.697 --> 00:23:00.194
They started going to the hills in Ozark and they were trying to dig tunnels in the sides of mountains.

00:23:00.195 --> 00:23:04.718
Tunnels like rabbit holes. Why? Because I want to show you this.

00:23:04.719 --> 00:23:12.798
Do you have it? The drones—remember the drones. I want you to listen to this noise.

00:23:12.799 --> 00:23:18.638
My son has this. I want you to listen to this. We've never used drones like this.

00:23:18.639 --> 00:23:25.916
I want you to pay very close attention to this. Those that are left, remember this because you don't have much time.

00:23:25.917 --> 00:23:33.410
Listen to this noise that you're about to hear. This is what you'll hear when you're left: over the skies, over the world.

00:23:33.411 --> 00:23:40.399
They will use these everywhere and there will be swarms of them. Why?

00:23:40.400 --> 00:23:47.330
Because they're going to look for if you have the chip in your forehead or your hand. And it sounds like this when it's coming.

00:23:47.331 --> 00:24:00.834
And the Christians that knew and tried to abstain and not get the mark—this is what it sounds like as they're coming.

00:24:00.835 --> 00:24:27.199
Do you hear it? They're preparing you. I said it sounds like bees.

00:24:27.200 --> 00:24:33.038
I could hear them from miles away as I was standing there with Jesus.

00:24:33.039 --> 00:24:37.783
And as they fly over, they were looking for people who didn't have the mark.

00:24:37.784 --> 00:24:53.038
And they surveilled the whole world. These will be everywhere. Okay, you can pause it.

00:24:53.039 --> 00:25:03.900
And as they find you, they scan your body and if it does not communicate back to them, one of those drones stays on you until the authorities get there.

00:25:03.901 --> 00:25:09.828
I saw you could not burn any wood because they would be able to sense fire.

00:25:09.829 --> 00:25:13.820
They would be able to hear a gunshot. They knew gunshot noise.

00:25:13.821 --> 00:25:29.519
So if you were trying to shoot game off the land to stay alive—elk, deer, rabbit, whatever you think you would need—if they heard the noise, they would go there and scan you and see who you were.

00:25:29.520 --> 00:25:33.645
The chip communicates, then they'd move on. If not, they stayed there.

00:25:33.646 --> 00:25:39.079
And I saw men with black Hummers, men with black masks, with blue lights.

00:25:39.080 --> 00:25:45.071
They jumped out of the cars and they gave you a decision. You had to make it right there.

00:25:45.072 --> 00:25:53.793
You either take the mark and serve the beast—you serve the Antichrist—or they cut your head off right there with a massive sword. They don't shoot you.

00:25:53.794 --> 00:26:06.914
